e of <LOCATION> Central </LOCATION> <LOCATION> America </LOCATION>'s poorest countries, had been an eye-opener. `` The children come running up to you for chocolate and money. And the way they live _ it makes you feel lucky to live in a house,'' said Spec. 4 <PERSON> James </PERSON> <PERSON> Holt </PERSON>, 20, of <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>. `` It makes you want to get back home so badly.''
