r can return.'' `` I'm sad about this problem,'' he said. `` My concern is that there were several hundred people out there and it is not right that maybe the lady that brought us hamburgers at three in the morning, or the guy who brought the sanitary privvies down _ how do you say they should not be in the movie, too?''
