<HEAD>US-Soviet Talks On Mideast Extended</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDS: Adds 4 grafs on report of Israeli practice bombing runs.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By BARRY SCHWEID</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Diplomatic Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
